<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦١٣٣ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5187">قُتَيْبَةُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5348">اللَّيْثُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4444">عُقَيْلٍ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5917">الزُّهْرِيِّ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2436">ابْنِ الْمُسَيَّبِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3320">أَبِي هُرَيْرَةَ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> أَنَّهُ قَالَ: <span class="c2">«لَا يُلْدَغُ الْمُؤْمِنُ مِنْ جُحْرٍ وَاحِدٍ مَرَّتَيْنِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>